    "Input highlights.",
    "Highlights show which parts of the input are important for the model to make its prediction.",
    "We use the Input×Gradient (Shrikumar et al., 2016) scores obtained with inseq (Sarti et al., 2023).",
    "We display the highlight scores by varying the color intensity of the important words.",
    "Higher scores correspond to more intense highlight colors presented to participants."
